ZH: 乖乖听话，不要闹了。
EN: Be good and obedient, stop making a fuss.

ZH: 孩子们都很乖，从来不给父母添麻烦。
EN: The children are all well-behaved and never cause trouble for their parents.

ZH: 乖一点，不要去惹老虎。
EN: Be good and don't provoke the tiger.

ZH: 他那张乖巧的脸庞让人很喜欢。
EN: His cute and well-behaved face is very likable.

ZH: 她的乖乖模样叫人看了很舒服。
EN: Her sweet and obedient appearance is very comforting to look at.

ZH: 你的小狗看起来真是乖乖的。
EN: Your puppy looks really well-behaved.

ZH: 希望今天一切顺利，大家都乖乖地完成任务。
EN: I hope everything goes smoothly today, and everyone completes the task obediently.

ZH: 请乖一点，不要再打扰别人。
EN: Please behave and stop bothering others.

ZH: 小猫那双乖巧的眼睛让人忍不住多看一眼。
EN: The kitten's cute eyes make people can't help but look more.

ZH: 他小小的个子，因此看上去更乖。
EN: His small stature makes him look even more obedient.

ZH: 这只小猫乖巧可爱，让人看了就喜欢。
EN: This little cat is cute and lovely, making people like it at first sight.

ZH: 她的乖巧讨喜让大家都很宠爱她。
EN: Her sweet and likeable personality makes everyone dote on her.

ZH: 狗狗看起来很乖，不会惹麻烦。
EN: The dog looks very well-behaved and won't cause trouble.

ZH: 她的外表看上去特别乖，让人很放心。
EN: Her appearance looks especially well-behaved, making people feel reassured.

ZH: 这份工作需要你乖巧的性格来完成。
EN: This job requires your obedient personality to complete.

ZH: 请乖乖待在这里，不要乱跑。
EN: Please stay here obediently and don't run around.

ZH: 我们需要一个乖乖听话的孩子来帮忙。
EN: We need a well-behaved and obedient child to help.

ZH: 快乖乖地坐好，别乱动。
EN: Sit down obediently and don't move around.

ZH: 那只小猫乖巧地站在那里，不敢动弹。
EN: The kitten stands there obediently, too scared to move.

ZH: 这只小鹿的乖巧模样让人感到温暖。
EN: The deer's obedient appearance makes people feel warm inside.
